description: Fuzion Eatz, we have a strong focus on Mediterranean and Middle Eastern flavors for our street food menus. We're two Sacramento area born business chefs/businessmen that are bringing a different twist on street food to Sacramento on their Gourmet Food truck. No tacos or burritos here folks, we serve Gourmet Wraps, Rolls and Bowls along with exciting sauces and toppings, fresh baked cookies and other walk and eat foods. Our mission is to serve quality gourmet grubs to our customers and to promote small business relationships. We are Fuzion Eatz!
name: Fuzion Eatz
